      <h2 style="font-family: Georgia, serif; font-size: clamp(22px, 3vw, 30px); font-weight: 700; color: #1C1C1E; line-height: 1.25; margin: 0 0 24px 0;">
        What are the schools like in Wilmslow?
      </h2>
      <p style="font-family: Inter, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75; color: #1C1C1E; margin: 0 0 16px 0;">Wilmslow has nine schools serving the town and surrounding villages, including two Outstanding-rated primary schools and a Good-rated secondary school (Ofsted, 2019-2025). The school density is higher than any other Golden Triangle town, making Wilmslow the default secondary catchment for families across the area.</p>

      <div style="overflow-x: auto; margin: 24px 0;">
        <table style="width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; font-family: Inter, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;">
          <thead>
