        <p style="font-family: Inter, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; color: #999999; margin: 8px 0 0 0;">Sources: <a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/ofsted" rel="nofollow noopener" target="_blank" style="color: #999999;">Ofsted</a>, 2019-2025. From September 2024, Ofsted no longer awards single overall grades for state schools.</p>
